From acd7e2f1d7da01637cf3facd1a048623289728e8 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Tasos Igglezakis <tasosigglezakis@gmail.com>
Date: Sat, 7 Feb 2026 13:36:55 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] mm: add EPT (Exposed Page Tables) subsystem

This patch introduces the EPT subsystem which exposes process page
tables to userspace via /dev/ept.

Signed-off-by: Tasos Igglezakis <tasosigglezakis@gmail.com>
